WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:02.919
Good morning, family, and welcome back.

00:00:02.919 --> 00:00:06.785
It's Brandon and Diana again, and we are blessed to have you here.

00:00:06.785 --> 00:00:09.350
We were looking forward to this, weren't we?

00:00:09.350 --> 00:00:13.582
I believe God has some work for us to do in the spirit realm.

00:00:16.386 --> 00:00:20.370
Somebody sent me a video from Kim Clement.

00:00:20.370 --> 00:00:22.830
They asked, 'Hey, did you see this, Brandon?

00:00:22.830 --> 00:00:23.933
Did you see this video?

00:00:23.933 --> 00:00:26.240
' I said, 'No, I've never seen this video before.

00:00:26.240 --> 00:00:28.898
' He talked about the oak tree.

00:00:30.568 --> 00:00:40.800
The Lord showed me four massive oak trees, and I've tried to interpret it myself the best I can because I still don't know what it means.

00:00:40.800 --> 00:00:54.092
I saw four oak trees and I thought it meant four years, but like I said, you do not assume you know anything or speculate about the spirit whenever it comes to what He's showing you.

00:00:54.092 --> 00:01:00.879
It takes time to pray it out, and He doesn't give you the whole interpretation all the time really quick.

00:01:00.879 --> 00:01:07.040
Sometimes it takes months; sometimes it may take years to get the whole thing.

00:01:07.040 --> 00:01:18.950
But when he came on there and started talking about the oak tree and a new energy source, I was like, 'What is this, the oak tree?

00:01:18.950 --> 00:01:23.560
' I'm like, that is not a coincidence that he's seeing an oak tree.

00:01:23.560 --> 00:01:36.076
I saw four massive oak trees and I thought, 'What is this, Lord, that You would show that man of God, before he went home to be with You, about the oak tree, and then You come and tell me four oak trees?

00:01:36.076 --> 00:02:12.760
' He didn't understand what he was seeing either; he didn't have the whole interpretation of it, but he saw oak trees, the acorn, and then he saw x p, but he didn't see the middle letter.

00:02:12.760 --> 00:02:42.973
Then the Lord showed me, while driving down the road, about x p, but I won't give the other one because this is not financial advice.

00:02:42.973 --> 00:03:02.490
But I saw that certain thing going above $10,000 and I saw it going to $5 quickly.

00:03:05.235 --> 00:03:30.659
The Lord told me that this would be big like Apple or Microsoft; it would be the new dot-com era that's coming, a new dot-com era was coming through digital platforms.

00:03:41.910 --> 00:03:42.300
It would be a supernatural wealth transfer coming through certain things.

00:03:53.932 --> 00:04:25.830
I'm telling you, ladies and gentlemen, I believe we are seeing President Trump step on the scene with Elon Musk, and we are seeing people who have a different way of thinking, who are not your average Joes, who have brilliant minds.

00:04:28.067 --> 00:05:00.875
The Lord told me there was a Solomon-type of an anointing that was coming on Trump in a greater magnitude in this next four-year term for the wealth of the sinner laid up for the just, and that it would come as they bless Israel.

00:05:15.600 --> 00:05:40.700
People don't like that part of it, but there was the covering of the blessing of Israel, like He said: 'Those that bless Israel, I will bless, and those that curse Israel, I will curse.

00:05:40.700 --> 00:05:53.800
' The blessing, as you bless Israel, comes on America in a different light.

00:06:00.749 --> 00:06:03.080
People say, 'I thought you saw a crash.

00:06:03.080 --> 00:06:06.587
' I did.

00:06:06.587 --> 00:06:12.310
Can some of that be averted?

00:06:22.129 --> 00:06:22.413
I have no idea.

00:06:22.413 --> 00:06:44.813
All I know is that I see a covering, and things are different when I pray over it now more than they've ever been, even more than earlier this year.

00:06:44.813 --> 00:06:49.129
Coming in 2024, the warnings that I was getting got pushed back.

00:07:09.526 --> 00:07:09.971
I'm telling you, it's been prayer.

00:07:09.971 --> 00:07:13.133
Prayer changes things.

00:07:13.133 --> 00:07:20.386
People go, 'Well, I don't understand that.

00:07:20.386 --> 00:07:33.780
' Well, you don't know the Spirit; you don't understand the Holy Spirit.

00:07:33.780 --> 00:07:39.270
You don't understand that the heartbeat of the Father is grace; the heartbeat of the Father is love.

00:07:50.149 --> 00:08:00.410
He's not a bully; He's not the mafia paying off the mafia with your tithe so the bully doesn't beat you up.

00:08:00.410 --> 00:08:15.137
Most people think, 'Well, I've got to do this so I rebuke the devourer.

00:08:15.137 --> 00:08:34.919
If I don't, then the devourer is going to eat me and the mafia is not going to protect me.

00:08:34.919 --> 00:09:02.465
' It's the mentality of how they see Him, as if He is not a God of love, but He's a God of judgment.

00:09:03.640 --> 00:09:13.600
People think God's mean, but God is a God of love.

00:09:23.858 --> 00:09:55.790
The more you fall in love with Him as your Father, as your great Creator, as your friend, as your El Elyon, as your Jehovah Jireh, as your everything that you know He is, the more He becomes real to you and you realize He is compassion.

00:09:55.790 --> 00:10:08.314
Yes, He's correction, but He says He corrects those He loves.

00:10:08.314 --> 00:10:22.176
Love never fails, and love sometimes is a spanking; we need it sometimes as the body of Christ.

00:10:22.176 --> 00:10:29.000
Judgment begins in the house of the Lord first.

00:10:29.000 --> 00:10:45.365
We see what the Scriptures say: 'If My people, who are called by My name, will humble themselves and pray.

00:10:45.365 --> 00:11:08.134
' But do we believe what the Scriptures say, that we will hear from heaven and He will heal our land?

00:11:08.134 --> 00:11:15.914
He said, 'I was watching the month of October.

00:11:15.914 --> 00:11:48.346
My people cry out for mercy in Washington and all around the world, praying for a God-fearing man, praying for a person that I had chosen to put in for such a time as this.

00:11:48.346 --> 00:12:04.600
' And now He said, 'I've heard that, and the balance of the scales—I've given you more time.

00:12:04.600 --> 00:12:13.320
' He's giving a season more of grace.

00:12:13.320 --> 00:12:22.720
He keeps talking about this four years.

00:12:22.720 --> 00:12:30.564
What are you going to do with the next four years?

00:12:30.564 --> 00:12:47.007
Are you going to go back into your slumber and your spiritual sleep, or are you going to win the lost?

00:12:47.007 --> 00:12:51.104
'I've given you some time.

00:13:17.279 --> 00:13:17.639
What will you do with this time?

00:13:34.700 --> 00:13:35.010
A reprieve,' He called it.

00:13:35.010 --> 00:13:42.680
'I'm giving you a reprieve, America.

00:13:42.680 --> 00:13:50.194
' I'm telling you, God is rich in Mercy.

00:14:03.380 --> 00:14:17.845
When we pray and He sees His kids praying, just like we do with our kids, how much more is our heavenly Father good to give good gifts to us?

00:14:32.483 --> 00:14:32.759
I think it's Matthew 7:11.

00:14:32.759 --> 00:14:50.906
He's not up there with a big hammer; He's going, 'Come to Daddy, I want to love on you.

00:14:50.906 --> 00:15:19.516
' He wants to have a passionate relationship with you where you wake up every morning and say, 'Good morning, Holy Spirit; good morning, Jesus; good morning, Father.

00:15:19.516 --> 00:15:30.182
' Now we see a window of blessing and what I've seen turn around in prayer.

00:15:34.755 --> 00:15:58.230
The enemy and his goons are trying to push their agenda against God's agenda, trying to speed up the Antichrist agenda, bringing a major world war.

00:16:04.360 --> 00:16:11.765
The Lord said, 'We want to stop this; we want a revival.

00:16:11.765 --> 00:16:25.989
' I've seen the house of cards fall; I've seen it come through the debt ceiling.

00:16:27.464 --> 00:16:49.320
But I'm telling you, after I saw what Prophet Kim Clement saw about x p and the oak tree back years ago, I thought, 'Lord, You've had a plan the whole time.

00:16:49.320 --> 00:17:12.257
' After some people have been praying over x p and the oak tree for over 10 years plus, I went, 'This has been a plan.

00:17:12.257 --> 00:17:28.490
' He gives us a little piece of the puzzle all of the time.

00:17:28.490 --> 00:17:46.920
Now we know what the middle letter is; we know it's x p and something else, but he didn't know.

00:17:46.920 --> 00:17:50.013
Isn't that amazing?

00:17:50.013 --> 00:18:00.355
Somebody sent us that in an email and it blessed me.

00:18:10.600 --> 00:18:11.000
It gives me clarity and confirmation.

00:18:11.000 --> 00:18:33.160
We still don't know what the oak tree represents, but I have a glimpse of what x p means to me.

00:18:33.160 --> 00:18:39.890
I'm praying over what it will do.

00:18:40.550 --> 00:19:22.234
The Lord is showing me that there is a wisdom on Trump to turn things around for the body of Christ, that we will have our window of revival and a glorious outpouring of the Spirit like we've never seen before.

00:19:22.234 --> 00:19:28.388
I saw a grace explosion.

00:19:28.388 --> 00:19:48.160
I saw transgender people sitting in the back because of the glory, people being desperate and hungry, wanting to experience the presence of the Lord.

00:19:48.160 --> 00:20:09.960
They were showing up to churches in their outfits and their rainbow-colored hair, taking those wigs off and weeping before the Lord.

00:20:09.960 --> 00:20:19.520
They were men dressed up like women, giving their hearts to Jesus Christ.

00:20:19.520 --> 00:20:57.700
Most churches are so anti-all-that, but the Lord said, 'Brandon, I desire for every man to have the opportunity to get born again—not to stay in the sin, but to have an opportunity to change.

00:20:57.700 --> 00:21:07.200
' People are just hurting and deceived, walking like a goose in the fog.

00:21:07.200 --> 00:21:27.484
All we have to do is bring the anointing of the Holy Spirit and be that salt and light, laying hands on the sick and seeing them recover.

00:21:51.614 --> 00:21:51.929
I saw major Hollywood stars come because of the revival, breaking the chains.

00:21:51.929 --> 00:22:38.965
They are seeking drugs and perversion to fill that void, but the only thing that's ever going to fill that void is Jesus Christ and the Holy Spirit.

00:22:38.965 --> 00:22:49.451
He came to set the captives free.

00:22:49.451 --> 00:23:20.819
I'm talking about a relationship like you have with your wife or husband, but even greater—a peace that passes all understanding.

00:23:20.819 --> 00:23:32.667
When they see that the healings are authentic and not put on...

00:23:32.667 --> 00:23:39.120
let's just be real.

00:23:39.120 --> 00:23:49.631
If you've got issues, let's work through them.

00:23:49.631 --> 00:23:55.580
Don't try to bury it.

00:23:55.580 --> 00:23:58.590
Just be real.

00:23:58.590 --> 00:24:09.599
When you get real with God, God will get real with you.

00:24:09.599 --> 00:24:16.220
Quit pretending and playing church.

00:24:16.220 --> 00:24:21.640
We're all a work in progress.

00:24:21.640 --> 00:24:30.424
Stop pretending and being full of pride.

00:24:30.424 --> 00:24:36.448
Get yourself right; come up higher.

00:24:36.448 --> 00:24:45.720
I just felt the Holy Spirit say all this.

00:24:45.720 --> 00:25:11.640
I had nothing really planned, but it came up out of me to tell you there's a great revival coming.

00:25:20.000 --> 00:25:21.460
The Lord called it a great grace explosion.

00:25:21.460 --> 00:25:34.000
He said, 'Where sin abounds, My grace does much more abound, Brandon.

00:25:34.000 --> 00:25:54.510
' He said, 'I'm going to give one last push, a great grace explosion, not judgment.

00:25:54.510 --> 00:26:08.313
' It's something beyond anything you can comprehend.

00:26:08.313 --> 00:26:19.999
We don't realize the compassion He has for us.

00:26:19.999 --> 00:26:41.879
It makes me go, 'Man, these people deserve hell,' but God said, 'I want to show them love.

00:26:41.879 --> 00:26:57.600
' Remember when the Sons of Thunder wanted to call down fire?

00:26:57.600 --> 00:27:00.320
He said, 'You don't know what spirit you are of.

00:27:00.320 --> 00:27:11.220
' He wanted to show them love.

00:27:11.220 --> 00:27:33.635
I've seen a great revival coming, and I know what the Lord is showing me about finances.

00:27:33.635 --> 00:27:41.142
There is a great blessing coming.

00:27:41.142 --> 00:27:59.660
We've got to pray against this war and the Antichrist agenda trying to stop the move of God.

00:27:59.660 --> 00:28:21.679
I believe we can turn things, just like He said He's giving us more time, a season of extended grace.

00:28:21.679 --> 00:28:36.513
He said, 'People will say you've missed it, but you haven't missed it.

00:28:36.513 --> 00:28:41.104
I've given more time.

00:28:41.104 --> 00:29:07.345
' There will be a major crash in the economy and the house of cards will fall, but do not rejoice when it falls; remain humble.

00:29:07.345 --> 00:29:23.012
If they ridicule you, just keep speaking what I want you to say.

00:29:23.012 --> 00:29:34.320
I know beyond a shadow of a doubt I've heard Him.

00:29:34.320 --> 00:29:54.968
I can miss timing just out of growing and learning, but when I say I've seen something, I don't fabricate it.

00:29:54.968 --> 00:30:10.069
Some of it you can stop with prayer and some of it you can't.

00:30:10.069 --> 00:30:21.666
It's for me realizing how much more God's grace is for us.

00:30:21.666 --> 00:30:51.703
He allowed me to see inside of Him, and I could see there was no beginning and no end.

00:30:51.703 --> 00:31:08.670
He said, 'I'm going to allow you to see in the depth of Me.

00:31:08.670 --> 00:31:20.588
' Those diamonds and sapphires, all those jewels on the crown of His head...

00:31:20.588 --> 00:31:24.733
I could see the glory.

00:31:38.010 --> 00:31:38.425
God is light, and in Him there is no darkness at all.

00:31:38.840 --> 00:32:06.052
The closest I've ever been was when He visited, and I said, 'Lord, You've got to veil this because I feel like my spiritual eyes are going to melt.

00:32:06.052 --> 00:32:26.419
' But I could see the dove come out of Him and flow over the top of us.

00:32:26.419 --> 00:32:35.733
I don't share all of this because it's private.

00:32:54.639 --> 00:32:54.999
The experiences we've had are priceless.

00:33:14.947 --> 00:33:18.679
I know most people would be jealous if I told them the depth of it, but I keep that private.

00:33:18.679 --> 00:33:20.707
Isn't Jesus wonderful?

00:33:20.707 --> 00:33:35.554
Lord, we know You love us, and we just yield to that love today.

00:33:35.554 --> 00:33:47.919
Become real to every single person watching through demonstrations and manifestations of Your glory.

00:33:47.919 --> 00:33:54.840
It will pop like popcorn, You said.

00:33:54.840 --> 00:33:58.869
'I will save Hollywood.

00:34:04.074 --> 00:34:05.017
I will save Elon Musk.

00:34:05.017 --> 00:34:14.999
' A great move of the Father is coming.

00:34:27.440 --> 00:34:29.639
Father, I thank You that we are the harvesters.

00:34:30.159 --> 00:34:40.270
You asked me, 'Will you help me bring in the harvest?

00:34:40.270 --> 00:34:48.064
' We will be bold for You.

00:34:50.879 --> 00:34:59.859
When we lay hands on the sick, we want to see results.

00:34:59.859 --> 00:35:29.390
We want to see the blinded eyes open, the deaf ears open, the lame leap, and those who weren't able to speak—their tongues will move again.

00:35:29.390 --> 00:35:38.320
Jesus is the same yesterday, today, and forever.

00:35:47.705 --> 00:36:00.355
We have a treasure in earthen vessels, that the excellency of the power will be known of You and not of us.

00:36:00.355 --> 00:36:06.795
Make that so real in our spirits today.

00:36:10.302 --> 00:36:12.800
We pick up the cross and follow You.

00:36:12.800 --> 00:36:30.950
If You'd use a donkey to warn the prophet, You can use me.

00:36:34.176 --> 00:36:45.176
We thank You for a fresh touch of Your Holy Spirit today.

00:36:45.176 --> 00:37:06.305
We want today's mana, a fresh manifestation of the glory on our houses.

00:37:13.147 --> 00:37:14.909
I want authentic—real authentic—in our lives.

00:37:18.343 --> 00:37:39.540
We take authority right now over this war and over the plans of the enemy through certain key leaders, from Emmanuel Macron to Putin to Biden.

00:37:39.540 --> 00:38:03.065
If it need be, like Ananias and Sapphira, I thank You that You would do whatever it takes for the removing of bad leadership.

00:38:03.065 --> 00:38:14.205
This will not take place, and millions of lives will be saved.

00:38:14.205 --> 00:38:25.367
I'm giving you extended grace for a harvest.

00:38:25.367 --> 00:38:53.291
We will see a mighty move of Your presence, even greater than what You did for the children of Israel.

00:38:53.291 --> 00:39:17.165
This will be the generation that ushers in the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ, the former and the latter rain together.

00:39:22.690 --> 00:39:39.800
We are going into the backfields to bring in the lost ones, going after the ninety-nine, going after the one.

00:39:39.800 --> 00:40:03.260
Give us a special anointing to minister to the lost and lay hands on the sick.

00:40:03.260 --> 00:40:16.879
We show that Jesus Christ is love and that He loves unconditionally.

00:40:32.225 --> 00:40:32.540
We call forth Elon Musk and Taylor Swift; we pray for their souls.

00:40:32.540 --> 00:40:45.289
They need to have a revelation that they need Jesus.

00:40:51.066 --> 00:41:02.307
The blinders are coming off of their eyes in the name of Jesus.

00:41:02.307 --> 00:41:11.670
They will use their celebrity for the glory of God.

00:41:11.670 --> 00:41:19.280
They'll be the biggest billboard for You.

00:41:20.600 --> 00:41:31.977
This is a time of great acceleration of seedtime and harvest.

00:41:31.977 --> 00:41:47.079
All the bad seeds we've sowed, we call crop failure over them in Jesus' name.

00:41:48.131 --> 00:41:53.099
We pray acceleration over the good seeds.

00:41:53.099 --> 00:42:00.714
People will say, 'How did this happen?

00:42:00.714 --> 00:42:07.409
' and we'll say, 'It was all Jesus.

00:42:07.409 --> 00:42:20.040
' I thank You that the people coming across Elon Musk's path are born again.

00:42:20.040 --> 00:42:28.740
Visit him even in the midnight hour.

00:42:37.928 --> 00:42:51.580
We will use Starlink to get the internet out to the people, and there will be a great transfer of knowledge from biblical principles.

00:43:09.240 --> 00:43:13.867
I thank You for a move of Your Spirit in Asia, in North Korea, South Korea, and over the underground churches in China.

00:43:33.656 --> 00:43:34.264
It would spread like fire all throughout Asia.

00:43:34.264 --> 00:43:40.964
Behold, You are doing a new thing.

00:43:40.964 --> 00:43:56.434
What are we going to do for this generation, for the millennials and all the younger people?

00:43:56.434 --> 00:44:00.090
