00:44:14.547 --> 00:44:14.873
They're like moths to a light.

00:44:30.599 --> 00:44:30.879
Father, we thank You that You will diffuse this war in Jesus' name.

00:44:40.119 --> 00:45:04.030
We ask for the Spirit of the Lord to move on Vladimir Putin's heart today and on Zelenskyy's heart today, that they come to an agreement of peace or remove the people out of the way.

00:45:04.030 --> 00:45:11.600
I pray wisdom over President Trump to turn things around.

00:45:11.600 --> 00:45:29.099
We call forth his advisers, even Elon Musk, that he would have supernatural wisdom to help bring America out of the hole.

00:45:29.099 --> 00:45:35.960
Make this country godly again, not just great again.

00:45:35.960 --> 00:45:45.989
Stir in the churches, the pulpits, the pastors, the prophets, and the evangelists.

00:45:45.989 --> 00:46:01.742
