00:46:39.639 --> 00:46:46.080
We take authority over any kind of terrorist attack or division.

00:46:53.227 --> 00:47:07.422
We call forth the FBI, CIA, and Homeland Security—the good, godly ones—to have supernatural wisdom on how to protect this nation.

00:47:07.422 --> 00:47:18.831
Divine protection over President Trump, his wife, his kids, and his grandkids.

00:47:18.831 --> 00:47:26.624
Let all corruption be brought to justice.

00:47:32.079 --> 00:47:39.133
It's like turning a light on in a kitchen and all the cockroaches scatter.

00:47:39.133 --> 00:47:51.103
We're swatting them with a big flyswatter, spraying them with Holy Ghost raid.

00:47:53.982 --> 00:48:02.467
We move the demonic strongholds, the principalities, and the powers out of the way.

00:48:02.467 --> 00:48:13.526
We will rise up and take our place like Joshua and Caleb.

00:48:13.526 --> 00:48:17.576
People will get a backbone.

00:48:28.671 --> 00:48:30.800
We pray over President Trump, and we thank You that Joe Biden goes and retires now.

00:48:32.276 --> 00:48:39.753
