00:50:02.535 --> 00:50:03.480
Amen.

00:50:13.062 --> 00:50:20.354
We pray for every one of you to have a healthy, blessed day.

00:50:20.354 --> 00:50:32.337
Whatever you have need of, Jesus paid the price.

00:50:53.474 --> 00:50:53.811
We call you delivered from all sickness and disease.

00:51:06.903 --> 00:51:07.354
We pray over every offering, 30, 60, 100-fold.

00:51:07.354 --> 00:51:17.599
We thank You that You anoint them to prosper.

00:51:17.599 --> 00:51:23.831
