A full-belly baby is a happy baby.

00:52:27.800 --> 00:52:37.220
Someone out there is believing for an adoption.

00:52:37.220 --> 00:52:51.805
We call the finances in for that and supernatural favor to find a child.

00:52:51.805 --> 00:52:54.799
Children are our inheritance.

00:52:54.799 --> 00:52:59.223
Doors will open where they need to.

00:53:08.098 --> 00:53:08.315
We stand with you today.

00:53:08.315 --> 00:53:24.480
Everybody who doesn't have a child but wants one, we stand for that—that they will conceive in the name of Jesus.

00:53:25.515 --> 00:53:30.280
The reproductive systems will function.

00:53:38.776 --> 00:53:43.215
The ovaries and the womb will be the perfect home for this baby.

00:53:43.215 --> 00:53:48.010
No cysts on the ovaries.

00:53:49.314 --> 00:53:57.286
We call for the fruit of the womb.

00:53:57.286 --> 00:54:09.799
I saw a Holy Ghost glow on the wombs of the women.

00:54:09.799 --> 00:54:20.787
No miscarriages; the anointing is going over your uterus right now.

00:54:20.787 --> 00:54:23.507
Polyps being dissolved.

00:54:23.507 --> 00:54:27.057
Generational curses broken.

00:54:27.057 --> 00:54:30.096
I heard polyps.

00:54:30.096 --> 00:54:41.579
So Father, we pray over the colons and the uteri—all polyps be dissolved.

00:54:54.440 --> 00:54:54.880
No cancer of the colon or uterus.

00:54:59.900 --> 00:55:00.090
I call healing over the sphincters.

00:55:00.090 --> 00:55:55.848
Yes, it's a uterus thing too—endometrial polyps.

00:55:55.848 --> 00:56:10.062
We call that to dissolve in the name of Jesus.

00:56:10.062 --> 00:56:11.982
Uterine polyps.

00:56:11.982 --> 00:56:15.530
We call them gone.

00:56:15.530 --> 00:56:18.240
Cycles to be regular.

00:56:18.240 --> 00:56:30.034
They will sleep soundly—no more torment or depression from SAD.

00:56:30.034 --> 00:56:33.866
Healing over thyroids.

00:56:33.866 --> 00:56:40.680
No Seasonal Affective Disorder.

00:56:40.680 --> 00:56:46.224
Their serotonin levels are normal.

00:56:57.906 --> 00:57:00.509
We speak life over your serotonin and dopamine.

00:57:00.509 --> 00:57:19.260
We command the spirit of depression to go.

00:58:28.813 --> 00:58:29.147
Be delivered from anxiety and fear.

00:58:29.147 --> 00:58:42.466
We renew our minds with the Word of God.

00:58:42.466 --> 00:58:52.767
We call for healing over people's legs—cramping and gout.

00:58:52.767 --> 00:59:40.675
I call healing over that calf and restoration over the knee joint, the cartilage, the tendons, and the ligaments.

00:59:40.675 --> 01:00:16.241
New joints in the name of Jesus.

01:00:18.945 --> 01:00:42.556
I see a rotator cuff being healed and whole, no more pain.

01:02:21.845 --> 01:02:22.411
We take authority over arthritis and rheumatoid arthritis in the hands and knuckles.

01:02:22.411 --> 01:02:28.776
Deliverance comes now.

01:02:28.776 --> 01:02:44.520
Blood disorders are being healed right now.

01:02:50.069 --> 01:03:02.069
The power of the Holy Spirit is driving out leukemia.

01:03:08.1000 --> 01:03:20.389
The fire of the Lord drives it out.

01:03:20.926 --> 01:03:23.311
I felt it.

01:03:33.839 --> 01:03:34.148
The Holy Spirit moved.

01:03:42.809 --> 01:03:43.064
It's Days of Heaven on Earth.

01:03:43.064 --> 01:03:45.119
They're coming.

01:03:45.119 --> 01:04:02.211
Watch what I'm going to do, says the Spirit of the Lord.

01:04:02.211 --> 01:04:08.389
Draw close to Me and come up higher.

01:04:08.389 --> 01:04:15.331
It's a time of great acceleration.

01:04:29.160 --> 01:04:29.345
It's time to soar.

01:04:29.345 --> 01:04:34.359
My perfect love will cast out that fear.

01:04:34.359 --> 01:04:41.135
Listen to Me; freshness will flow.

01:04:41.135 --> 01:04:51.490
Go into all the world and bring deliverance to the captives.

01:04:51.490 --> 01:04:59.753
It will require you to come up higher every day.

01:04:59.753 --> 01:05:02.674
It needs consistency.

01:05:16.340 --> 01:05:16.704
I want to dedicate my time for that too—consistency.

01:05:16.704 --> 01:05:19.206
Well, I'm glad I showed up today.

01:05:35.040 --> 01:05:35.500
I hope you are too.

01:05:35.500 --> 01:05:45.879
If you're new here, we do prayer every day.

01:05:45.879 --> 01:06:01.359
If you could please like our video and subscribe, click the notification bell.

01:06:05.311 --> 01:06:05.533
It helps with the algorithm.

01:06:05.533 --> 01:06:12.440
We're trying so hard to grow a million-prayer army.

01:06:12.440 --> 01:06:26.382
The Lord said, 'I've mandated you to do prayer every day to have a million people.

01:06:26.382 --> 01:06:30.371
' We can change things.

01:06:42.640 --> 01:06:42.840
For many—what did he say yesterday?

01:06:42.840 --> 01:06:46.511
—'Many hands make light work.

01:06:46.511 --> 01:06:49.417
' We're stronger together.

01:07:03.698 --> 01:07:18.240
I believe it's time for us to be together and not be divided by all kinds of doctrines of demons, but just rising up and being one body.

01:07:18.240 --> 01:07:30.599
I remember Tommy Hicks—I don't remember his name, I think it was him—who had the vision of the giant rising up and the body became one.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
It was an end-time vision he had.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.950
I believe with all my heart that Jesus is about to do something we've never seen before.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
Isn't it exciting that He picked you and me and my wife?

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.550
He said to me, 'Brandon, you're the generation that will not taste death.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
' Jesus is coming.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
Jesus loves you so much.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
God bless you all, and we'll see you again tomorrow.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Bye-bye.
